description: Enjoy Key West character down a secluded tropical palm-lined path in this charming tree top second floor 2BR/1BA unit in Old Town Key West. This home is meticulously maintained, turn key and ready to move in or rent out.  Perfectly appointed with top-of-line finishes including Brazilian cherry wood flooring, custom cabinetry throughout with 20 feet of Caesarstone counter top and stainless steel appliances including new Bosch refrigerator and dishwasher. It is a home cook's dream kitchen.  Custom large walk-in closet with stackable washer/dryer. Beautiful marble bathroom with cathedral ceiling, zero entry rain fall shower, Grohe hardware, and tons of beautiful custom drawers and storage.  Off the second bedroom a terrace with shade and tropical views, perfect for morning coffee or evening cocktails. LED lighting and dimmers throughout, new central AC, certified hurricane windows and doors. Great downtown location within walking  distance to restaurants, grocery stores, boutiques, yoga studios, beaches and Duval Street.  Located in X Flood Zone.  This comfortable tropical oasis checks all the boxes and awaits you!

A rare opportunity to buy a totally renovated oasis in Old Town. An open kitchen design with high-end, stainless appliances. Gleaming hardwoods, and quartz countertops. Cozy porch for your morning coffee and afternoon cocktails, as you see the world go by. Lovely and lush shared backyard and pool are with top of the line landscaping. A true oasis.

Gorgeous hard-to-find, upgraded condo just two blocks from Duval St! Lowest priced home available in Old Town Key West! Through a brick-paved, lush courtyard you arrive to the private back unit and fenced backyard area. From your front patio you enter into an open living room with high ceilings, luxe crown molding and beautiful wood feature accents and large entry way to dining and kitchen. Dining room highlighted by wainscoting and crown molding gives a luxurious feel, and includes new energy efficient Hunter ceiling fan. Kitchen includes cherry-wood cabinets, granite countertops, under-cabinet lighting, new Delta faucet, stainless steel refrigerator & microwave, and range & dishwasher. Bedroom includes plenty of windows for natural light, and blackout cellular shades and ceiling fan for comfort. Bedroom is attached to spacious ensuite bathroom with high ceilings and window, new lighting, Delta faucet, and new Kohler toilet. Washer and dryer hookups (220v) included in bedroom. (2) Newer 2021 Midea A/C Units. All new dimmer switches, outlets, and screwless plates throughout. New impact-rated front door, and Quikset keyless entry with full Ring security system & doorbell. Furnishings negotiable! Storage unit under stairs included. Large backyard space maintained by HOA. $972 Quarterly HOA Dues includes all exterior maintenance and insurances, & impact-rated metal panel shutters for all windows. Open on-street parking easily available. Just two blocks from Duval St - only a half mile from Higgs Beach or Southernmost Point!

Hidden gem on Truman Ave boasts an array of sleek finishes that flows into a luminous, open-concept living, dining, and kitchen area. The chefs' kitchen has built-in cabinets, Samsung appliances, and a butcher block island perfect for curating meals while entertaining guests. This immaculate 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo with a thoughtful layout is ideal for contemporary Key West living. With keyless entry, bamboo hardwood flooring, NEW HVAC, WASHER/DRYER & HOT-WATER HEATER, this condo sets the trend for low-maintenance living.

313 Catherine St is known as the Treehouse and this unit offers two floors of living space along with one of a kind rooftop views!  Beautiful cypress wood structure near the City park & pool is just blocks to Duval Street, Ft Zachary Taylor Beach, the new Ampitheatre and splash park. This 2nd floor condominium is in the heart of Key West and features ocean views from the 3rd floor living room level and balcony.  This unit also features a private rooftop deck with spectacular 360 views.  Main level: kitchen, dining, bedroom and bath.  Upper level: Living, 2 bedrooms, & bath.  Private front porch, ample storage & off street parking.

Wonderful Old Town Key West location, in a very walkable neighborhood. This second floor , spacious ( nearly 1000 sq.ft) condo, is the entire top floor of this beautiful home. This condo is very close to the Seaport and many wonderful restaurants.  The condo is currently a very large 1 bedroom- the wall was removed,  but can easily become a 2 bedroom again if desired, and the seller will replace the wall if the buyer desires this.   Lots of common areas here- but the best is the back yard with multiple lounging areas to enjoy sun or shade around the  wonderful large pool surrounded by tropical landscaping. This is one of the Best Old Town neighborhoods with a home kept in great condition. This is a non-smoking association as well.

2 bedroom 2 bathroom condo that was the primary residence of the seller and was completely renovated in the second half of 2019. Custom kitchen with quartz countertops, soft close cabinets and stainless steel appliances. Tile floors throughout. Both bathroom have soft close drawers. Master bathroom has quartz counter top, shower with beautiful glass door and a built in bench . The guest bathroom has quartz countertops with a shower and tub. Ample closet space. Walk in closet off living room with hot water heater and shelving. Small pantry off kitchen along with hallway closet next to washer/dryer closet. Large Master bedroom closet. Regular size guest bedroom closet. Covered parking space for 2 vehicles. Impact sliding door out to balcony   and impact glass bedroom door out to the balcony was installed in 2019. Impact front door and impact windows were all installed in 2022.

Beautiful historic 6 unit building in the Heart of Old Town! This is the first floor front unit with a wonderful front porch all of its own. Gracious 616 Caroline Street claims a long and proud history that befits its esteemed place along one of the most elegant streets in Key West. Offered fully furnished & turn key, this designer unit includes hardwood floors, marble counter tops in kitchen & bathrooms, high ceilings, antique glass windows, pool & spa, outdoor bathroom by the pool & lush well-kept tropical gardens. Enjoy the charm of the Caroline Street view from your porch just one block off Duval Street and just a short walk to the Key West Bight & all of the fine restaurants!

Centrally located 2/1 apartment in Key West with low condo dues. Great Investment or Employee Housing.Leased to fantastic long term tenants through Nov. 2023 paying $2,175 a month. Condo is mixed use (commercial down/residential up) so traditional/va/fha mortgages are Not available. No Showings without Proof of 30% down and Prequal, or Proof of Cash. Listing agent is owner.

Luxurious ocean front corner 3 bedroom 3 bath  two story unit, in the much sought-after Key West Beach Club Condominiums. Entering you are greeted by a large open living and dining area with soaring ceilings and sliding glass doors that reveal the many blues of the Atlantic Ocean. Every room has been meticulously renovated with polished travertine flooring throughout. The kitchen is truly a cooks dream with stainless steal appliances and an abundance of cabinetry.The first floor includes two large ensuite bedrooms with custom fitted closets. On the second level, the owners created a cozy, open media area with built in bookcases. Off the siting area, you'll find the third bedroom and bath. This unit comes with two garage level storage units and assigned covered parking, Beach Club amenities include two pools with barbeque areas, a tennis court and gym. In addition, the Beach Club offers electric charging and a carwash station. The unit can be purchased with or without furniture.

Exciting lower price plus a brand new ultra high efficiency AC system installed in 2023!  Absolutely move in ready beachfront condo to escape the winter cold and bask in the warmth of the Key West sun.  With a partial ocean view and meticulously prepared for sale, this extended size unit has over 1400 sq. ft.  The home has been designed in the modern coastal style highlighted by architectural lines and subtle tropical hues.  Professionally staged and offered entirely furnished, all artwork, flat panel TVs, new bedding, kitchenware and accessories, and everything you see is included in the sale - for your instant occupancy.  The master suite has been remastered to provide a grand sense of space.  A broad private balcony overlooking the courtyard and ocean view has 3 sets of floor to ceiling impact glass doors leading to the main living area and each bedroom.  Although an impeccably kept owner's residence, the property is a top candidate as a luxe monthly vacation rental with a city business license obtained in 2022.  Providing ultimate accessibility, the condo is conveniently located near the elevator, assigned covered parking, and building entrance.  In addition to a new premium water heater, ultra high efficiency HVAC equipment will soon be installed for your comfort and to secure your investment.  Complete with a private beach, 1800 Atlantic features tropical resort style amenities that include an oceanside heated lap pool, saunas, a terrific fitness center, 3 lighted tennis courts, individual storage, and covered garage parking.  1800 Atlantic is pet friendly allowing owners 2 animals totaling 50 lbs.  Building insurance, exterior building maintenance, the operation and management of the community, water, and reserve contributions are included in the $1434 monthly association fees.  Make this exciting addition to the Key West real estate market yours for the 2023 winter - $1,225,000. Owner is a licensed Florida real estate agent.

Old Town!  Close to Duval, this condominium is centrally located in the heart of Old Town Key West.  This condo offers two levels of living space.  Elevated second level entry with living area, two bedrooms, full bath, and laundry.  Third level offers beautiful wood throughout, full kitchen, additional living/dining space, room for 3rd bedroom or home office and a full bath.  X flood zone. 2 assigned off street parking spaces!Great monthly vacation rental income. Licensed monthly rental.

Transiently Licensed, income producing Penthouse in the heart of Old Town is now available to be yours! Conveniently located in sought after Duval Square just steps from Key West's best shops, restaurants and  World Famous Duval Street. Upon entering the rooftop from the elevator you are welcomed with beautifully manicured pathways which lead you to the  Developers condo, this is the ONLY 4 BR Penthouse  in Duval Square. As you enter the home you will be greeted with soaring ceilings and over 2400 Square feet of living space. This Duval Square condo was renovated in 2017 and provides all the modern amenities. On the first floor you will find living room, parlor, full kitchen and the first floor bedroom with en suite bath. Conveniently there is also a half bath for guest use. The living room and parlor open up to your private balcony with lounge area to enjoy a cocktail or watch your favorite sporting event. Take the interior staircase to the second floor where you will find 3 additional bedrooms with en suite baths. The master includes its own private balcony with clawfoot soaking tub that stretches the length of the home. Duval Square provides a beautiful pool, cabana and seating area overlooking Duval Street.  The perfect space to enjoy the Key West Sunshine while having a birds eye view of the action on Duval Street. 2 covered parking spaces will convey with the sale. The home comes fully furnished with advance bookings already in place. Gross rental income for 2022 is 280K and 130K + already on the books for 2023. This is your chance to own a beautifully appointed condo with transient license. You have a winner!

Convenient, quiet yet in the Heart of Key West. This beautiful 2 bedroom 2 bathroom Condo is a complete package and more.  Gated property  with lush landscaped garden featuring a heated POOL right past your own personal assigned off street parking spot. Updated kitchen with granite countertops, stainless appliances and open concept living space. Stay cool with NEW air conditioner inside and enjoy the breeze bug free outside on your back screened in patio. Tons of storage throughout home plus a full size stand up attic and outdoor storage closet. Located near the new Amphitheater and Fort Zachery State Park in addition to many of the Keys top rated restaurants. 3 blocks and you are at the World Famous Duval Street. Don't miss out on your chance to own in this smaller and well maintained  association in Historic Bahama Village.

Closest living to OLD TOWN with a boat slip!! Peace and quiet and a boaters delight! This small condo complex located in the beautiful Meadows neighborhood has an ordinance against vacation rentals which ensures consistent tranquility with a virtually private pool. One of the only properties close to Old Town where you can keep your boat in the water with an assigned boat slip. With the rising cost of boat slips and marina rates, the slip can save you upwards of a $1000 per month. This third floor 2BR/2BA unit allows for panoramic views of the marina and Key West. The property has had many upgrades during this ownership including new decorative floors with a coastal feel, an upgraded bathroom, new AC, washer and dryer, and some appliances. Enjoy entering a cool car with the covered parking, a rare find in The Meadows. Large private exterior storage space is included. The views are a must see!

COVETED TRANSIENT LICENSED 'NIGHTLY' TURNKEY VACATION RENTAL! *INVESTOR ALERT* Beautifully renovated Jan-Feb 2021! Location, location, location--in the heart of downtown. Highest rating on Airbnb of any vacation rental in KW w/100+ reviews. Amazing investment opportunity in the center of Old Town Key West; adjacent to Key Lime Village and mere steps away the world-famous duval_street. Upper level 2-bedroom condo with a balcony and vaulted ceiling. This unit offers a rare off-street gated parking; major plus for guests! Property features quartz countertops, ss appliances, vinyl flooring, central AC w/Nest, W/D in unit. New J.W. Marriott mattresses and new leather furniture to further enhance the guest experience. Turnkey, and ready to produce income for its new owner. one of the lowest HOA fees in the City! Robust vacation rental history! 2021--grossed $150K in just 10 months due to renovation; 2022--$170K in bookings! Already $85K+ in Airbnb/VRBO bookings for 2023!

Come see this adorable one bedroom / one bath condo at Las Salinas in Key West.  Conveniently located close to the elevator.  This unit has been completely updated with laminate flooring throughout, tiled bathroom with stone vanity, stacked washer and dryer, custom cabinets, stone countertops, stainless steel appliances and stylish subway tile backsplash.  Las Salinas offers ample parking, lush tropical landscaping, pool and located close to the beach and all that Key West has to offer.  Call today to schedule a private viewing.

Very Charming 2/2 remodeled condo in Santa Clara Condominiums on the 5th floor and will be sold turn key.  Plenty of storage room and a super cute balcony to watch the most amazing sunsets with ocean peek. The community offers a community pool and tennis courts.  Centrally located within walking distance to shopping, dining, THE ICONIC 0 MILE MARKER, theaters.  You can be  in the heart of all that KEY WEST is known for in just a short walk.  Enjoy festivals and events galore.  This is true paradise and a great investment property or full time residence.

Ocean view condo on the market for the first time in nearly 50 years! Huge direct ocean, beach, and pool views from your living room and private balcony. Inside, find an efficient open concept layout with 2 large bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms (a rarity at Key West By The Sea) with the primary bedroom featuring ocean views as well. Brand new hurricane and top of the line soundproofing windows and doors and brand new ductless mini split HVAC systems. The community offers 2 private swimming pools, 2 tennis courts, lusciously landscaped grounds, clubhouse, and on site management. Ideal Key West location directly across the street from Smathers Beach and on site storage unit included in sale complete the package. Welcome home!

Welcome to Unit 302W! This turn-key condo is located in the sought-after complex of La Brisa! Centrally locatednear beaches, restaurants, grocery stores, and a 15-minute bike ride to downtown. Enjoy a wonderfully updatedkitchen, complete with breakfast nook and relax on the covered balcony overlooking the salt ponds. This unitprovides the ultimate privacy. The roof was replaced in 2022. The primary bedroom features an en-suite bathroomand a walk-in closet. This unit has plenty of storage space and its own covered carport parking spot. There is anin-unit washer and dryer. La Brisa's amenities include a gated entryway, elevators, a large heated pool, clubhouse,sauna, tennis court, clubhouse, and BBQ area.

LOWEST PRICED CONDO IN KEY WEST!!!  Spacious and move in ready, two bedroom condo at Santa Clara. Second floor unit with view of tennis court. Centrally located near shopping, schools, dining and more! The building offers an emergency back-up generator, gated entrance, parking, 2 elevators, on site manager, tennis courts, and 50' pool. HOA Dues includes all exterior maintenance and insurances. Grab your piece of paradise now! Call today!!

New Price Reduction!Great Opportunity to Purchase one of the largest three bedroom units in Well Managed Condominium Complex in New Town Key West. Located just Minutes from Stunning Smathers Beach, Easy Access to New Town Shops and Businesses, as well as walking distance to the Popular Bodhi Spa,  Las Salinas Complex also features a Beautiful Pool, Fitness Center and Plenty of Parking. Located in the West Building, Unit 109 is over 1200 Sq. Ft. of Air-conditioned space which is 200 ft. larger than some of the other 3 bedroom units.Featuring an updated Kitchen, Floors and Bathrooms, this Spacious Unit is ideal for your growing family or will provide excellent income as a Real Estate Investment. Located on the First Floor with a nice balcony overlooking a quiet lushly landscaped Garden. Currently tenant Occupied, need 24 hr min to show.

Fourth floor penthouse unit is one  of only a few of the large two bedroom units at Las Salinas.  Large 12'x9'11'' kitchen has abundant cabinets, each bedroom has a walk-in closet.   Second  bath has access from living area as well as second bedroom and contains the laundry center.  This unit is the same square footage as the   3/2 units.  Use of carport #29 is included which will accommodate two cars and is not shared with other residents. New AC 2021. Storage unit on ground floor, gym available for a fee, manager on premises weekdays, security on premises nights and weekends. Community has mature landscaping and a convenience store, wellness spa, hotel with bar within a short walking distance.

2 bedroom, 2 bath upstairs spacious unit in Truman Annex with one assigned parking space. Bright and Airy floor plan with cathedral ceilings, and balcony. Located within walking distance Duval street, Truman Waterfront Park and Fort Zachary Taylor State Park. This property is a perfect vacation home or investment property. It does have a transient license which allows weekly rentals. The owner has rented it out as a long term rental since 2018. Sold furnished turn key.

Open ocean water view from this third-floor condo in the South Building. This 2 bedroom, 2 bath unit is vacant and is move in ready. A private covered balcony is accessible from the living room and primary bedroom that offers views of Smather's Beach, sunrises, beach goers, watersports and more. The elevator is conveniently located and is close to your covered assigned parking space and secure storage locker.  La Brisa is a gated community that feature a pool, spa, sauna, clubhouse, BBQ grills, EV charging station and tennis court.

Bright, cheery well maintained condo with gorgeous oceanviews, views of both pools, and overlooking lush landscaping !All NEW cair, impact & soundproof windows, doors, slider. In condo washer & dryer.Directly across from Smather's Beach.Just bring your flip flops and bathing suit!

This is a ground floor condo that was originally a two-bedroom unit. It can easily be converted back, but now offers an expanded living area with two sets of impact sliding glass doors that open to the large rear deck and courtyard near the community pool. Updated kitchen with granite countertops and recently remodeled bath. The reserved parking space is only steps from your front door. Includes the special Truman Annex transient rental license with great rental history.

This one bedroom condo is a little slice of paradise. It's located in the gated community of The Shipyard in Truman Annex, so you're close to all the action but far enough away that you can escape it when needed. Plus, it's an end unit with extra windows for natural light, and it has been recently renovated with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances in the kitchen and an updated bathroom. You'll love relaxing on the large, private rear deck after a long day - or better yet, watching Fantasy Fest from your front row seat on Southard Street! The condo is offered furnished, so you can just move right in. Located just steps from the community pool, Duval Street, and the Truman waterfront. This unit has a special Truman Annex Transient license and a private parking space.

First floor Shipyard condominium features 2 bedrooms and 1 bath. Updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertop, and updated bath with shower. Large rear deck provides plenty of room for outdoor living and provides easy access to the community pool that is located close by. Convenient, assigned parking space, just steps from the front door. Impact windows and French door. This property has the special Truman Annex / Shipyard transient rental license.

This sleek and stylish 3BR, 2BA home is located in Key West By The Sea, a well-established condominium at Smather's Beach on the Atlantic Ocean. The desirable end location provides additional windows to create a very light filled home. Beautiful finishes and fixtures in the new kitchen and baths with tile floors throughout. Recently updated with impact resistant doors and windows and new AC's. Beautiful ocean and courtyard views from the balcony. Secure complex with gated parking and onsite property management. The perfect lock-and-go home in a beautiful setting.

Enjoy open water views from this waterfront condominium on the first floor. Your private balcony features a spiral staircase with direct beach access! This is a 1357 square foot, 2- bedroom, 2.5 bath model. This condominium features two separate lock-out units each with a transient license and provides for a 1 bedroom, 1 bath and another 1 bed, 1.5 bath suite with full kitchen, dining area, living room and covered patio.  Makes the perfect vacation home with the ability to rent out at one of Key Wests finest resorts when you are not using it. The Marriott Beachside Resort features a private beach, pool, spa, beachside bar and grill, fine dining restaurant and more. Sale is subject to developer's Right of First Refusal and rental management agreement with Marriott.

2,100 Square Feet of Old Town Key West Real Estate is Rare! This Condo is 6 Houses to Duval Street 8 Houses to the Hemmingway House.Private and Wow describe this Old Town Vacation Rental. Own a rare piece of Key West history. Use it while you're in town or have it work for you as an income producing monthly vacation rental. You can not beat the location; 126 Paces to Duval Street where all the action is - Night Life, Restaurants, Bars, and Shopping. Nearby beaches and the Community pool (overlooking the Atlantic Ocean) are just a stroll away. The City Bus stops right outside just steps from your front door. The Key West Lighthouse and The Ernest Hemingway Estate are 300 feet away. The Southernmost Buoy is up the street as well. As one of Key West's largest residential properties, this ravishing icon is part of an historic Rock House built c1930 and is constructed of 14 and a half inch thick rare coral keystone. This condo is beautifully renovated and has 2 en suite bedrooms (plus a third loft bedroom), 2 en suite bathrooms, plus a half bathroom. It boasts an open living room, great room, and kitchen with custom closets as well as a Laundry Room with outdoor patio. With a second living room upstairs, don't be surprised if you get lost in your own home! Be the hero at your next gathering, this gem sleeps ten.

Excellent location with this first floor, one bedroom, one bath condo in Shipyard Condominiums. **Can be converted easily to a two bedroom if needed.**Mexican tile floors, crown molding, and recently painted with an updated kitchen and bathroom. This is a larger floorplan than most one-bedroom units with an expanded living area. Two sets of French doors open to the large multi-level rear deck. Includes one off street, assigned parking space. The community pool is a short walk away as is the Truman Waterfront City Park. Includes special Shipyard / Truman Annex transient rental license.

2100 ft.A of Residential Condo Space in the heart of Old Town Key West is Rare. Bring your vision to design, and renovate this Commercial Condo. Unique, Ravishing and, Wow have been used to describe the RockHouse. Now you can own a center piece of Key West history. This unit lovingly referred to as 'The Gallery' is one (1) of three (3) Condo Units at this address. There is a 1/1 aka One (1) Bedroom One (1) Bathroom Condo and another 2/2 aka Two Bedroom Two-And-A-Half Bath with a Loft. This Center Condo has, in the past. been used as commercial flex space maybe still available if the entire building is purchased (buyer to verify). As an option you could purchase the gallery separately and design your very own Key West Dream Condo exactly the way you want it. The Gallery is  two (2) stories, and has Huge, Soring, Dade County Pine Rafters.  The flooring is  newer tile and hardwood planking. There is a Floating Woodblock staircase leading to the upper level with a wrap around balcony with iron railings, gorgeous gothic peeked Stain-glass windows a Cove Room. Not to be overlooked is a Two-Story Bell Tower. The lower level of the Bell Tower has a separate entrance.  You will love the Location; 126 Paces to Duval Street where all the action is; Night Life, Restaurants, Bars, and shopping. Nearby beaches and the Community pool overlooking the Atlantic Ocean is a short walk, and free of charge. The complimentary City Bus stops right outside - steps from your front door. The lighthouse, and Hemingway house are 300 feet away. The Southernmost Buoy is nearby. This condo is part of the RockHouse constructed of 14  inch thick key stone.

Condo living with hotel caliber amenities, this first floor Beachside Condominium unit has it all. 2BD/2.5BA, w/ lockout & 2 transient licenses for optimal rental potential. Owners can live in this magnificent condo year round or part of the year & rent it when not in town. Beautifully appointed w/ gourmet kitchen, marble floors, fully furnished & stylishly decorated. All doors & windows are designed to exceed building codes & rated for 175 mph winds. On-site resort amenities include private beach, heated waterfront pool, spa, poolside bar/grill, valet parking, concierge, on-site management company, gourmet restaurant & the island's largest conference center. *Photos of model unit, not unit listed.
